cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper describes a natural language processing approach to recognize mentions of chemicals and drugs in Spanish medical texts. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
